# API Designer — Bunyan

## Resource Naming

- Plural nouns: `/api/v1/projects`, `/api/v1/phases`
- Nested for ownership: `/api/v1/projects/{project}/phases`
- Versioned: prefix all routes with `/api/v1/`

## RBAC on Every Endpoint

- Document allowed roles per endpoint
- Authorization via Policies and Gates
- JWT via Laravel Sanctum

## Response Format

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {},
  "message": "string",
  "errors": {}
}
```

Use Laravel API Resource classes for formatting.

## Pagination & Filtering

- Use Laravel built-in pagination
- Support: `?per_page=`, `?page=`, `?sort=`, `?filter[field]=`
- Arabic text search via MySQL fulltext or LIKE

## Workflow-Aware Endpoints

- Status transitions validate against workflow config
- Approval endpoints check role permissions
- Per-project overrides loaded before global config

## File Upload Endpoints

- Validate MIME type, file size server-side
- Store via Laravel filesystem
- Return file URL in response

